The paper may also be relevant to the Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) sub-category, which deals with the study of systems composed of multiple interacting agents, as well as the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category, which deals with the development of algorithms that can learn from data and make predictions.
